<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Yena's Parlour · P&amp;P 분석 연습장</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Libre+Baskerville:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/variable/pretendardvariable.min.css">
<style>
:root{
  --paper:#F7F6F1; --card:#FFFFFF; --ink:#232A33; --soft:#5A6472;
  --wg:#5B7BA6; --wg-deep:#3E5E8C; --wg-pale:#E9EEF5; --line:#CBD6E4;
  --seal:#95392F; --seal-deep:#7A2C24; --gilt:#A8842C; --gilt-pale:#F5EFDE;
  --ok:#4C7A5A;
  --en:'Libre Baskerville', Georgia, serif;
  --ko:'Pretendard Variable',Pretendard,'Noto Sans KR',-apple-system,sans-serif;
  --sans:'Pretendard Variable',Pretendard,'Noto Sans KR',-apple-system,sans-serif;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;}
body{margin:0; background:var(--paper); color:var(--ink); font-family:var(--sans); font-size:15.5px; line-height:1.7;}
.wrap{max-width:760px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 16px 100px;}
header{padding:24px 0 8px; text-align:center;}
.eb{font-size:12px; letter-spacing:.22em; color:var(--wg-deep); text-transform:uppercase;}
h1{font-family:var(--en); font-weight:400; font-size:clamp(25px,6vw,36px); margin:5px 0 2px;}
.sub{font-family:var(--sans); color:var(--soft); font-size:14.5px; margin-bottom:12px;}
nav{position:sticky; top:0; z-index:30; background:rgba(247,246,241,.95); backdrop-filter:blur(6px); display:flex; gap:6px; padding:10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); margin-bottom:16px; overflow-x:auto;}
nav button{flex:1 0 auto; border:1px solid var(--line); background:var(--card); color:var(--soft); padding:8px 14px; border-radius:999px; font-size:14px; font-weight:500; cursor:pointer; white-space:nowrap; font-family:var(--sans);}
nav button.on{background:var(--wg-deep); border-color:var(--wg-deep); color:#fff;}
nav button:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--seal); outline-offset:2px;}
.panel{display:none;} .panel.on{display:block; animation:fade .22s ease;}
@keyframes fade{from{opacity:0; transform:translateY(4px);} to{opacity:1;}}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.panel.on{animation:none;}}
h2{font-family:var(--sans); font-size:18.5px; margin:20px 0 8px;}
.note{font-size:14px; color:var(--soft);}
.chips{display:flex; gap:6px; overflow-x:auto; padding:4px 0 10px;}
.chips button{border:1px solid var(--line); background:#fff; border-radius:999px; padding:6px 14px; font-size:14px; cursor:pointer; white-space:nowrap; color:var(--soft); font-family:var(--sans);}
.chips button.on{background:var(--ink); color:#fff; border-color:var(--ink);}
.chips select.vsec{border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:999px; padding:6px 12px; font-size:13.5px; font-family:var(--sans); background:#fff; color:var(--soft); max-width:230px;}
.search{width:100%; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:999px; padding:10px 16px; font-size:15px; font-family:var(--sans); background:#fff; margin-bottom:10px; color:var(--ink);}
.search:focus{outline:2px solid var(--wg);}

/* vocab */
.fcard{background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:14px; min-height:225px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; text-align:center; padding:24px; cursor:pointer; position:relative; box-shadow:0 1px 0 var(--line);}
.fcard .tag{position:absolute; top:12px; left:14px; font-size:12px; letter-spacing:.13em; color:var(--wg-deep); text-transform:uppercase;}
.fcard .box{position:absolute; top:12px; right:14px; font-size:12px; color:var(--soft);}
.fcard .word{font-family:var(--en); font-size:33px;}
.fcard .pos{color:var(--soft); font-style:italic; font-size:13px;}
.fcard .def{font-size:16px; max-width:460px;}
.fcard .kr{font-family:var(--sans); font-weight:600; color:var(--wg-deep); font-size:17px; margin-top:6px;}
.fcard .hint{position:absolute; bottom:10px; font-size:12px; color:var(--soft);}
.fbtns{display:flex; gap:10px; margin-top:12px;}
.fbtns button{flex:1; padding:11px; border-radius:10px; border:none; font-size:14px; font-weight:700; cursor:pointer; font-family:var(--sans);}
.b-again{background:#fff; border:1.5px solid var(--gilt); color:var(--gilt);}
.b-know{background:var(--wg-deep); color:#fff;}
.fmeta{display:flex; justify-content:space-between; font-size:13px; color:var(--soft); margin-top:8px;}
.vrow{padding:10px 4px; border-bottom:1px dashed var(--line); font-size:14.5px;}
.vrow b{font-family:var(--en); font-size:16.5px;}
.vrow .st{float:right; color:var(--ok); font-size:13px;}
.quizq{background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:12px; padding:16px;}
.quizq .qw{font-family:var(--en); font-size:24px; margin-bottom:10px;}
.quizq button{display:block; width:100%; text-align:left; margin:6px 0; padding:11px 13px; border-radius:9px; border:1px solid var(--line); background:#fff; font-size:15px; cursor:pointer; font-family:var(--sans);}
.quizq button.right{background:#EAF3EC; border-color:var(--ok);}
.quizq button.wrong{background:#F6E8E6; border-color:var(--seal);}
.toolrow{display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:center; margin-bottom:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;}
.tbtn{border:1px solid var(--line); background:#fff; border-radius:9px; padding:8px 13px; font-size:14px; cursor:pointer; color:var(--soft); font-family:var(--sans);}
.pcount{margin-left:auto; font-size:13.5px; color:var(--soft);}

/* shared cards */
.bgc{background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:12px; margin:10px 0; overflow:hidden;}
.bgc>button{width:100%; text-align:left; background:none; border:none; padding:13px 15px; cursor:pointer; display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:baseline; font-family:var(--sans);}
.bgc .cat{font-size:12px; letter-spacing:.1em; color:var(--gilt); font-weight:700; white-space:nowrap;}
.bgc .ttl{font-family:var(--sans); font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:var(--ink); flex:1;}
.bgc .arr{color:var(--soft); font-size:12px;}
.bgc .body{display:none; padding:0 15px 14px; border-top:1px dashed var(--line);}
.bgc.open .body{display:block;}
.bgc .body p{font-size:15px; margin:10px 0;}
.usebox{background:var(--gilt-pale); border-left:3px solid var(--gilt); padding:9px 13px; font-size:14px; border-radius:0 8px 8px 0; margin-top:8px;}
.usebox b{color:var(--gilt);}

/* lenses */
.lenscard{background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:12px; margin:10px 0; overflow:hidden;}
.lenscard>button{width:100%; text-align:left; background:none; border:none; padding:13px 15px; cursor:pointer; display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:center; font-family:var(--sans);}
.lenscard .em{font-size:22px;}
.lenscard .ln{font-family:var(--sans); font-weight:700; font-size:16.5px;}
.lenscard .ls{font-size:13.5px; color:var(--soft); font-family:var(--sans);}
.lenscard .body{display:none; padding:0 15px 15px; border-top:1px dashed var(--line);}
.lenscard.open .body{display:block;}
.stem{background:var(--wg-pale); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:8px; padding:9px 12px; font-family:var(--en); font-size:14.5px; margin:6px 0; cursor:pointer;}
.stem:hover{border-color:var(--wg);}
.mv{font-size:14.5px; margin:6px 0; padding-left:18px; position:relative;}
.mv:before{content:"？"; position:absolute; left:0; color:var(--seal); font-weight:700; font-size:12px;}
.tchips{display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:6px; margin-top:8px;}
.tchip{font-size:13px; background:#fff; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:999px; padding:3px 10px; color:var(--wg-deep); font-family:var(--en);}
.trbox{background:#F1F4EE; border-left:3px solid var(--ok); padding:9px 13px; font-size:14px; border-radius:0 8px 8px 0; margin-top:10px;}
.lh{font-size:13px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.1em; color:var(--soft); margin:12px 0 4px; text-transform:uppercase;}

/* scenes */
.scl{background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:12px; padding:13px 15px; margin:9px 0; cursor:pointer; display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:baseline;}
.scl:hover{border-color:var(--wg);}
.scl .ch{font-family:var(--en); color:var(--wg-deep); font-size:13.5px; white-space:nowrap;}
.scl .st{font-family:var(--sans); font-weight:700; font-size:15.5px; flex:1;}
.back{border:none; background:none; color:var(--wg-deep); font-size:14.5px; cursor:pointer; padding:4px 0; font-family:var(--sans);}
.scene-set{font-family:var(--sans); color:var(--soft); font-size:15px; margin:4px 0 14px;}
.qb{background:#FFFDF8; border:1px solid #E3DCC8; border-radius:3px; padding:13px 15px; margin:9px 0; position:relative;}
.qb:before{content:""; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; right:0; height:4px; background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,var(--line) 0 8px, transparent 8px 14px);}
.qb .en{font-family:var(--en); font-size:15px; line-height:1.7;}
.qb .en .tg{color:var(--seal); font-style:normal; font-family:var(--sans); font-weight:700; font-size:13px; letter-spacing:.04em;}
.qb .kr{font-size:13.5px; color:var(--wg-deep); margin-top:6px; padding-top:6px; border-top:1px dashed #E3DCC8;}
textarea{width:100%; min-height:80px; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:9px; padding:10px 12px; font-family:var(--sans); font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; background:#fff; resize:vertical; margin-top:6px; color:var(--ink);}
textarea:focus{outline:2px solid var(--wg); border-color:var(--wg);}
.qbox{background:var(--wg-pale); border-radius:10px; padding:13px 15px; font-size:14.5px; margin:16px 0 4px;}
.qbox b{color:var(--wg-deep);}
.sealwrap{text-align:center; margin:18px 0 6px;}
.sealbtn{width:78px; height:78px; border-radius:50%; border:none; cursor:pointer; color:#F3E3DC; font-family:var(--en); font-size:12px; line-height:1.15; background:radial-gradient(circle at 32% 30%, #B5544A, var(--seal) 55%, var(--seal-deep)); box-shadow:0 3px 8px rgba(122,44,36,.4), inset 0 0 0 4px rgba(255,255,255,.08); transition:transform .15s;}
.sealbtn:hover{transform:scale(1.05);}
.seallabel{font-size:13px; color:var(--soft); margin-top:6px;}
.model{display:none; background:var(--gilt-pale); border:1px solid var(--gilt); border-radius:12px; padding:14px 16px; margin:12px 0;}
.model.open{display:block; animation:fade .25s;}
.model .mlens{font-size:13px; font-weight:700; color:var(--gilt); letter-spacing:.08em; margin-bottom:8px;}
.model .pl{display:flex; gap:9px; margin:8px 0; font-size:15px; line-height:1.7;}
.model .pk{font-family:var(--en); color:var(--seal); font-weight:700; min-width:16px;}
.model .mko{font-family:var(--sans); font-size:14px; color:var(--seal-deep); margin-top:10px; padding-top:10px; border-top:1px dashed var(--gilt);}
.drill{background:#F1F4EE; border:1px solid #C9D6C5; border-radius:10px; padding:13px 15px; margin:14px 0; font-size:14.5px;}
.drill b{color:var(--ok);}

/* builder */
.builder label{font-weight:700; font-size:14.5px; display:block; margin-top:14px;}
.builder label span{font-weight:400; color:var(--soft); font-size:13px;}
.assembled{background:#FFFDF8; border:1px solid #E3DCC8; border-radius:10px; padding:16px; font-size:15.5px; line-height:1.75; margin-top:14px; white-space:pre-wrap; font-family:var(--en);}
.btnrow{display:flex; gap:8px; margin-top:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;}
.solid{padding:10px 16px; border-radius:9px; border:none; background:var(--ink); color:#fff; cursor:pointer; font-size:14px; font-family:var(--sans);}
.ghost{padding:10px 16px; border-radius:9px; border:1px solid var(--line); background:#fff; color:var(--soft); cursor:pointer; font-size:14px; font-family:var(--sans);}
.draft{background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:10px; padding:12px 14px; margin:8px 0; font-size:14px;}
.draft .dh{display:flex; justify-content:space-between; color:var(--soft); font-size:12.5px; margin-bottom:4px;}
.draft .dx{color:var(--seal); cursor:pointer; background:none; border:none; font-size:12px; font-family:var(--sans);}

/* gloss & phrases */
.grow{padding:10px 4px; border-bottom:1px dashed var(--line); font-size:14.5px;}
.grow b{font-family:var(--en); font-size:16px;}
.grow .gk{color:var(--wg-deep);}
.grow .gx{color:var(--soft); font-size:13.5px;}
.pgroup{margin:14px 0;}
.pgroup h3{font-family:var(--sans); font-size:15px; margin:0 0 6px; color:var(--seal-deep);}
.shield{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; background:var(--gilt-pale); border:1px solid var(--gilt); border-radius:11px; padding:9px 13px; margin-bottom:16px;}
.shield .sh-l{font-size:13.5px; font-weight:700; color:var(--gilt);}
.shield select{flex:1; min-width:150px; border:1px solid var(--gilt); border-radius:8px; padding:8px 10px; font-size:14px; font-family:var(--sans); background:#fff; color:var(--ink);}
.locknote{background:#F4F1EA; border:1px dashed var(--gilt); border-radius:9px; padding:11px 13px; font-size:13.5px; color:var(--soft); margin:10px 0;}
.locknote button{margin-left:8px; border:1px solid var(--gilt); background:#fff; color:var(--gilt); border-radius:7px; padding:4px 11px; font-size:12.5px; cursor:pointer; font-family:var(--sans);}
.scl.locked{opacity:.62;}
.lockhint{font-size:12px; color:var(--gilt); white-space:nowrap;}
.scwarn{background:#F4F1EA; border:1px dashed var(--gilt); border-radius:9px; padding:10px 13px; font-size:13.5px; color:var(--soft); margin:8px 0 4px;}
.gx-lock{color:var(--gilt); cursor:pointer; font-size:13px;}
.cmp{background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:12px; margin:10px 0; overflow:hidden;}
.cmp.now{border-color:var(--wg-deep); box-shadow:0 0 0 1px var(--wg-deep);}
.cmp>button{width:100%; text-align:left; background:none; border:none; padding:13px 15px; cursor:pointer; display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:baseline; font-family:var(--sans);}
.cmp .rng{font-family:var(--en); color:var(--wg-deep); font-size:13.5px; white-space:nowrap;}
.cmp .ct{font-weight:700; font-size:15.5px; flex:1;}
.cmp .stt{font-size:12px; white-space:nowrap;}
.cmp .stt.done{color:var(--ok);} .cmp .stt.now{color:var(--wg-deep); font-weight:700;} .cmp .stt.todo{color:var(--soft);}
.cmp .body{display:none; padding:0 15px 14px; border-top:1px dashed var(--line);}
.cmp.open .body{display:block;}
.cmp .before{font-size:14.5px; margin:11px 0;}
.cmp .wf{font-size:14px; margin:6px 0; padding-left:22px; position:relative;}
.cmp .wf:before{content:"👀"; position:absolute; left:0; font-size:12px;}
.charcard{background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:12px; margin:10px 0; padding:13px 15px;}
.charcard .cn{font-family:var(--en); font-size:17px; font-weight:700;}
.charcard .ck{color:var(--wg-deep); font-size:14px; font-weight:600;}
.charcard .ctag{font-size:12.5px; color:var(--gilt); font-weight:700; margin-left:6px;}
.charcard .crel{font-size:13px; color:var(--soft); margin:3px 0 7px;}
.charcard .cbase{font-size:14.5px;}
.clayer{background:var(--gilt-pale); border-left:3px solid var(--gilt); border-radius:0 8px 8px 0; padding:9px 12px; font-size:14px; margin-top:8px;}
.clayer.lk{background:#F4F1EA; border-left-color:var(--line); color:var(--soft); cursor:pointer; font-size:13px;}
.cgroup{font-size:13px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.08em; color:var(--soft); margin:18px 0 4px; text-transform:uppercase;}
.savestat{position:fixed; bottom:14px; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%); background:var(--ink); color:#fff; font-size:13px; padding:6px 14px; border-radius:999px; opacity:0; transition:opacity .3s; pointer-events:none; z-index:50;}
.savestat.show{opacity:.92;}
.empty{text-align:center; color:var(--soft); padding:28px 10px; font-size:14px;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
<header>
  <div class="eb">Yena's Parlour · Analysis Dojo</div>
  <h1>Pride &amp; Prejudice <span style="font-size:.55em">분석 연습장</span></h1>
  <div class="sub">목표는 P&amp;P가 아니라, 어떤 작품을 만나도 통하는 분석의 힘 — P&amp;P는 연습 상대</div>
</header>

<nav role="tablist">
  <button class="on" data-tab="t-compass">나침반</button>
  <button data-tab="t-chars">인물</button>
  <button data-tab="t-vocab">어휘</button>
  <button data-tab="t-bg">배경지식</button>
  <button data-tab="t-lens">분석 렌즈</button>
  <button data-tab="t-scene">장면 분석</button>
  <button data-tab="t-build">빌더</button>
  <button data-tab="t-ref">용어·표현</button>
</nav>
<div class="shield">
  <span class="sh-l">📖 진도 방패 — 어디까지 읽었나요?</span>
  <select id="shsel"></select>
</div>

<section id="t-compass" class="panel on">
  <div class="note">구간마다 ① <b>읽기 전</b> 스포일러 없는 안내 → ② <b>읽으면서</b> 주목할 것 → ③ <b>읽은 뒤</b> 확인 질문(자동 저장). 진도 방패를 올리면 ✓ 표시가 따라옵니다.</div>
  <div id="comparea"></div>
</section>

<section id="t-chars" class="panel">
  <div class="note">처음 읽는 사람을 위한 인명록. 기본 소개는 스포일러 없음 — 인물의 <b>뒷면</b>은 진도에 따라 한 겹씩 열립니다.</div>
  <div id="chararea"></div>
</section>

<section id="t-vocab" class="panel">
  <div class="chips" id="vscope"></div>
  <input class="search" id="vsearch" type="search" placeholder="단어 검색 (예: countenance, 편견, irony)…">
  <div class="toolrow">
    <button class="tbtn" data-vm="cards">카드</button>
    <button class="tbtn" data-vm="list">목록</button>
    <button class="tbtn" data-vm="quiz">퀴즈</button>
    <button class="tbtn" id="vshuffle">↺ 섞기</button>
    <span class="pcount" id="vprog"></span>
  </div>
  <div id="varea"></div>
</section>

<section id="t-bg" class="panel">
  <div class="note">소설 '내용'이 아니라 분석에 필요한 '맥락'만 모았어요. 각 카드 끝의 <b style="color:var(--gilt)">분석에 이렇게 쓴다</b>가 핵심.</div>
  <div class="chips" id="bgcat"></div>
  <div id="bgarea"></div>
</section>

<section id="t-lens" class="panel">
  <div class="note">렌즈 = 분석 문장의 <b>주어를 정하는 법</b>. 같은 장면도 렌즈를 바꾸면 다른 논점이 나옵니다. 문장 스템을 탭하면 빌더의 P칸으로 들어가요. 맨 아래 <b style="color:var(--ok)">전이</b>는 다른 작품에 옮겨 쓰는 법.</div>
  <div id="lensarea"></div>
</section>

<section id="t-scene" class="panel">
  <div id="scenehome">
    <div class="note">원문 대신 <b>핵심 인용 은행</b>만. 순서: 인용을 소리 내어 읽기 → 연습 질문에 직접 쓰기 → 봉인을 깨고 모범 PETAL과 비교 → 변주 드릴로 렌즈 갈아끼우기.</div>
    <div id="scenelist"></div>
  </div>
  <div id="sceneview" style="display:none"></div>
</section>

<section id="t-build" class="panel">
  <h2>PETAL 빌더</h2>
  <div class="note">렌즈를 고르면 그 렌즈의 문장 스템과 기법 칩이 나타나요. 스템 탭 → P칸에 삽입, 기법 칩 탭 → T칸에 삽입.</div>
  <div class="chips" id="blens"></div>
  <div id="bstems"></div>
  <div class="builder" id="bform"></div>
  <div class="assembled" id="basm"></div>
  <div class="btnrow">
    <button class="solid" id="bcopy">단락 복사</button>
    <button class="ghost" id="bsave">드래프트 저장</button>
